<div class="story">
<p>Roanoke Shore is a soundside subdivision in Nags Head consisting of roughly 41 properties of which 5 are soundfront. There is a community sound access for the rest of the properties and the beach is not too far away. The homes on north side of the subdivision border the golf course in the <a href="https://www.outerbankshome.com/outer banks/real estate/nags head/village-at-nags-head.asp" title="Village at Nags Head">Village at Nags Head</a>. </p>
